    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>if you set locale to ar_SA it will have date array returns instead of integer, if you changed the locale to 'ar' or 'ar_JO' it will work normally.</p>

<p>I got the following two lines code from magento 1.6.2:</p>

<p>$filter = new Zend_Filter_LocalizedToNormalized(array('locale' =&gt; 'ar_SA'));
$cartData[$index]['qty'] = $filter-&gt;filter(5);</p>

<p>to fix this issue I have removed the following block from ar_SA.xml</p>

<p>#0.###;#0.###-</p>

<p>and everything worked normally now.</p>

    </div>
